PrecisAmendment to the ABANDONMENT OF BRANCH LINES PROHIBITION ORDER NO. 3 which terminates the protection from abandonment affecting a 15.5 mile section of the CN PADDOCKWOOD SUBDIVISION in Saskatchewan, between White Star and Paddockwood, since there is no longer any traffic originating or terminating on this segment.
